trans-unit.source: Provides constants for compatibility with the Visual Basic 6.0 <xref uid="langword_csharp_ZOrder" name="ZOrder" href=""></xref> method.
trans-unit.target: Fornisce costanti per la compatibilità con Visual Basic 6.0 <xref uid="langword_csharp_ZOrder" name="ZOrder" href=""> </xref> metodo.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], the Visual Basic `ZOrder` method is replaced by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.BringToFront%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.SendToBack%2A> functions.
trans-unit.target: In [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], Visual Basic `ZOrder` (metodo) viene sostituito il <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.BringToFront%2A>e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.SendToBack%2A>funzioni.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.SendToBack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.BringToFront%2A>

trans-unit.source: These constants enable code that has been upgraded from Visual Basic 6.0 to continue to run without additional modification.
trans-unit.target: Queste costanti consentono al codice che è stato aggiornato da Visual Basic 6.0 di continuare l'esecuzione senza modifiche aggiuntive.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Functions and objects in the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6> namespace are provided for use by the tools for upgrading from Visual Basic 6.0 to [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Funzioni e gli oggetti di <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>dello spazio dei nomi sono destinati all'utilizzo con gli strumenti per l'aggiornamento da Visual Basic 6.0 a [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>

trans-unit.source: In most cases, these functions and objects duplicate functionality that you can find in other namespaces in the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Nella maggior parte dei casi, queste funzioni e oggetti duplicano funzionalità disponibili in altri spazi dei nomi di [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: They are necessary only when the Visual Basic 6.0 code model differs significantly from the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] implementation.
trans-unit.target: E sono necessari solo quando il modello di codice Visual Basic 6.0 è notevolmente diverso rispetto di [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] implementazione.

trans-unit.source: Equivalent to the Visual Basic 6.0 constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbBringToFront" name="vbBringToFront" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Equivalente alla costante di Visual Basic 6.0 <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbBringToFront" name="vbBringToFront" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Equivalent to the Visual Basic 6.0 constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbSend ToBack" name="vbSend ToBack" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Equivalente alla costante di Visual Basic 6.0 <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbSend ToBack" name="vbSend ToBack" href=""> </xref>.
